00:16:10,098 --> 00:16:11,832
Jiji!

253
00:16:11,865 --> 00:16:12,965
What's wrong?!

254
00:16:13,532 --> 00:16:14,665
Ah! A monster!

255
00:16:14,698 --> 00:16:15,432
Jiji!

256
00:16:16,232 --> 00:16:17,998
Whoa! What's a
monster doing
here!

257
00:16:18,032 --> 00:16:19,165
Jiji!

258
00:16:22,265 --> 00:16:23,765
(painful screaming)

259
00:16:26,632 --> 00:16:28,198
Yuichiro!

260
00:16:28,798 --> 00:16:30,032
Jiji!

261
00:16:31,032 --> 00:16:32,798
Go! Get out
of here, Rei!

262
00:16:32,832 --> 00:16:33,765
But Yuichiro!

263
00:16:33,798 --> 00:16:36,898
