266
00:16:41,632 --> 00:16:43,665
(painful screams)

267
00:16:44,032 --> 00:16:46,898
Rei, please go!
Get away!

268
00:16:47,765 --> 00:16:49,432
Yuichiro!

269
00:16:52,998 --> 00:16:57,632
Rin! Pyo! To!
Sha! Kai! Jin!
Retsu! Zai! Zen!

270
00:16:57,965 --> 00:16:59,065
<i>Jiji!</i>

271
00:17:01,732 --> 00:17:02,865
Rei!

272
00:17:02,898 --> 00:17:06,532
