273
00:17:06,565 --> 00:17:07,698
Jiji!

274
00:17:08,732 --> 00:17:10,865
How in the world
did this happen
to you, Grandpa?!

275
00:17:10,898 --> 00:17:11,898
Jiji!

276
00:17:11,932 --> 00:17:13,132
How awful!

277
00:17:13,165 --> 00:17:15,665
Jiji!

278
00:17:18,432 --> 00:17:19,665
Jiji!

279
00:17:19,698 --> 00:17:20,632
No! Stop!

280
00:17:21,165 --> 00:17:22,498
Jiji!

281
00:17:24,832 --> 00:17:25,965
(growling)

282
00:17:26,532 --> 00:17:27,898
Jiji!

283
00:17:28,632 --> 00:17:29,632
Grandpa!

284
00:17:31,165 --> 00:17:33,732
You've gotta snap
out of it! It's
me, your dear
granddaughter, Rei!

285
00:17:33,765 --> 00:17:35,132
You remember,
don't you?!

286
00:17:35,165 --> 00:17:36,865
Jiji!

287
00:17:36,898 --> 00:17:40,098
I know you're being
possessed by something.
Because if any of your
kind heart were still

288
00:17:40,132 --> 00:17:44,032
in there, you wouldn't
be so evil and keep
attacking me like you
are right now!

289
00:17:44,065 --> 00:17:45,865
Ji-Jiji?

290
00:17:45,898 --> 00:17:47,798
Can you hear me?

291
00:17:50,998 --> 00:17:52,065
Jiji!

292
00:17:52,098 --> 00:17:53,932
Wha!! Well that
didn't work!

293
00:17:53,965 --> 00:17:55,732
Jiji!

294
00:17:59,165 --> 00:18:00,498
You stop that!

295
00:18:01,898 --> 00:18:04,665
If you think I'm
gonna let you pick
on my dear friend
Rei, you've got

296
00:18:04,698 --> 00:18:06,098
another thing
coming!

297
00:18:06,132 --> 00:18:10,765
Moon Prism Power!
Make Up!

298
00:18:40,665 --> 00:18:44,498
I am the Pretty
Guardian who fights
for love and for
justice!

299
00:18:44,532 --> 00:18:46,432
I am Sailor Moon!

300
00:18:46,465 --> 00:18:50,965
And now, in the
name of the moon,
I'll punish you!

301
00:18:50,998 --> 00:18:52,665
Jiji...

302
00:18:52,698 --> 00:18:54,565
You really saved
me, thank you.

303
00:18:54,598 --> 00:18:57,698
My pleasure! By
the way, have you
had one of these
daifuku? They're

304
00:18:57,732 --> 00:18:59,032
just really
delicious,
you'll love it!

305
00:18:59,065 --> 00:19:00,498
Huh?

306
00:19:00,532 --> 00:19:03,965
Have you completely
lost it?! This is
not the time to be
eating daifuku!

307
00:19:03,998 --> 00:19:07,432
Oh, you're right.
Okay, now!

308
00:19:07,632 --> 00:19:11,432
Wait, hold it!
somewhere inside
that evil creature
is my Grandpa!

309
00:19:11,465 --> 00:19:13,765
Huh?! Really?!

310
00:19:13,798 --> 00:19:16,498
That monster's
your Grandpa?!

311
00:19:16,898 --> 00:19:21,665
I get it! He was
acting strange because
these changes were
already underway!

312
00:19:21,698 --> 00:19:22,865
Jiji!

313
00:19:22,898 --> 00:19:25,765
(scared screaming)

314
00:19:27,032 --> 00:19:28,298
Jiji!

315
00:19:28,565 --> 00:19:30,232
Ahhh!

316
00:19:30,698 --> 00:19:32,532
Ahhh!

317
00:19:33,032 --> 00:19:36,998
If that scary monster
is Rei's Grandpa, we
have a problem!

318
00:19:37,032 --> 00:19:41,265
Rei, use you talisman!
It'll stop that monster
from chasing us!

319
00:19:41,298 --> 00:19:41,932
Jiji!

320
00:19:41,965 --> 00:19:43,765
Right! That will
wake him up!

321
00:19:43,798 --> 00:19:46,365
Evil spirit!
Be exorcized!

322
00:19:48,332 --> 00:19:49,798
Jiji!

323
00:19:51,932 --> 00:19:54,332
Sailor Moon,
do it! Quickly!

324
00:19:54,365 --> 00:19:56,665
Jiji!!

325
00:19:56,698 --> 00:20:00,365
Okay Gramps, turn
back into a good
guy!

326
00:20:00,832 --> 00:20:06,332
Moon Healing
Escalation!

327
00:20:06,965 --> 00:20:09,298
Jiji!

328
00:20:09,332 --> 00:20:11,965
Refresh!

329
00:20:14,565 --> 00:20:17,598
Ahhhh...

330
00:20:17,632 --> 00:20:19,232
Oh, Grandpa!

331
00:20:23,365 --> 00:20:25,232
So it worked...

332
00:20:25,265 --> 00:20:26,598
Yeah...

333
00:20:28,998 --> 00:20:30,498
Oh...
Mako!

334
00:20:30,532 --> 00:20:33,532
Hey, Ami! So where
are you off to?

335
00:20:33,565 --> 00:20:37,532
I just can't stop
thinking about the
fight that Rei had
with Usagi. I was

336
00:20:37,565 --> 00:20:40,865
hoping we could
talk Rei into
forgiving her and
being friends again.

337
00:20:40,898 --> 00:20:42,932
You know, I thought
the same thing.

338
00:20:42,965 --> 00:20:44,932
Great! Then we've
gotta help them.

339
00:20:44,965 --> 00:20:48,598
Once there's a
problem, friendships
between girls can
crack and fall apart

340
00:20:48,632 --> 00:20:52,898
quick. So I think the
sooner we get those
two seeing eye to eye
again, the better.

341
00:20:52,932 --> 00:20:54,032
Um-hm!

342
00:20:57,898 --> 00:21:01,232
Boy! You're right,
these daifuku are
tasty!

343
00:21:01,265 --> 00:21:02,632
I told you!

344
00:21:02,665 --> 00:21:05,932
By the way, where
did that strange
monster end up
going anyway?

345
00:21:05,965 --> 00:21:07,098
What strange
monster?

346
00:21:07,132 --> 00:21:09,865
Oh c'mon! You mean
you don't remember
what you did to-

347
00:21:09,898 --> 00:21:14,365
Ha-ha-ha! Monster?
What monster? There
are no monsters here
right, Usagi?

348
00:21:15,198 --> 00:21:18,798
Yuichiro, you must've
just had a bad dream
or something about
monsters!

349
00:21:18,832 --> 00:21:19,932
Yeah! A bad
dream!

350
00:21:19,965 --> 00:21:23,498
You think so? It
sure didn't feel
like a dream to me.

351
00:21:23,932 --> 00:21:26,732
Oh well, whatever!
Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha-ha!

352
00:21:27,265 --> 00:21:29,165
Hey Yuichiro...

353
00:21:29,465 --> 00:21:31,065
Huh?

354
00:21:31,098 --> 00:21:34,565
You might seem like
a big blockhead, but
inside, you're a guy
who's really very kind

355
00:21:34,598 --> 00:21:35,565
and brave!

356
00:21:35,598 --> 00:21:36,398
Hah!

357
00:21:38,398 --> 00:21:43,198
Ahh! Now I feel
alive with youth and
all it's wonder!

358
00:21:43,498 --> 00:21:44,732
Ha-ha-ha!

359
00:21:44,765 --> 00:21:47,798
Rei's in love with
Yuichiro! Aren't
you, you sly little
minx?

360
00:21:47,832 --> 00:21:51,465
Huh?! Don't be
silly! I'm not in
love with him! It's
just that Grandpa's

361
00:21:51,498 --> 00:21:54,198
always telling him
