felt bad for him!

362
00:21:54,232 --> 00:21:55,565
Sure you do!

363
00:21:55,598 --> 00:21:57,065
You've got it
all wrong!

364
00:21:57,098 --> 00:22:00,698
Rei! I'm not going
to let you marry
Yuichiro! You'll
have to tell him no!

365
00:22:00,732 --> 00:22:01,765
Huh?

366
00:22:01,798 --> 00:22:03,632
Marry him Rei!
Marry him!

367
00:22:03,665 --> 00:22:04,832
Hey! Stop
saying that!

368
00:22:04,865 --> 00:22:06,332
